OL,5,G0330 Citizen Smith
OL,6,     FThe Hostage: Following a
OL,7,     Fby-election humiliation in which
OL,8,     Fhe gained a mere 6 votes, Wolfie
OL,9,     Fplans to kidnap the Conservative
OL,10,     Fwho beat him. There's nothing as
OL,11,     Fbad as democracy!
OL,12,G0400 Citizen Smith
OL,13,     FThe Path of True Love: When a
OL,14,     Fcustomer starts chatting up
OL,15,     FShirley in the shop, she decides
OL,16,     Fto move on from Wolfie - which
OL,17,     Fmeans the fearless leader may have
OL,18,     Fto move out of her spare room.
