OL,13,     FSpeed's Return: Speed is due out
OL,14,     Fof prison after an 18-month
OL,15,     Fsentence, and Wolfie's not looking
OL,16,     Fforward to informing him that his
OL,17,     Flong-term girlfriend is pregnant.
